# SaaS Platform — Data Model

## Entities

### Entity: Organization

A workspace that contains projects and members.

```yaml
entity: Organization
type: entity
properties:
  id:
    type: string
    required: true
  name:
    type: string
    required: true
  plan:
    type: enum
    required: true
    values: [free, pro, enterprise]
  seats:
    type: number
    required: true
    default: 1
states: [active, suspended, deleted]
lifecycle: active → suspended → deleted
```

### Entity: User

A person with access to one or more organizations.

```yaml
entity: User
type: entity
properties:
  id:
    type: string
    required: true
  email:
    type: string
    required: true
  name:
    type: string
    required: true
  role:
    type: enum
    required: true
    values: [owner, admin, member]
states: [active, invited, suspended]
lifecycle: invited → active → suspended
```

### Entity: Subscription

Billing plan for an organization.

```yaml
entity: Subscription
type: entity
properties:
  id:
    type: string
    required: true
  plan:
    type: enum
    required: true
    values: [free, pro, enterprise]
  price_cents:
    type: number
    required: true
  billing_cycle:
    type: enum
    required: true
    values: [monthly, annual]
states: [active, past_due, canceled]
lifecycle: active → past_due → canceled
```

### Relationship: Organization → User

```yaml
relationship: Organization → User
verb: has_member
cardinality: N:N
required: true
```

### Relationship: Organization → Subscription

```yaml
relationship: Organization → Subscription
verb: has
cardinality: 1:1
required: true
```
